```csv
"File","Concept","Sentence","Prompt"
"01-futuristic-city-skyline-1-","Futuristic city skyline","In the year 2050, cities looked very different.","futuristic city skyline with floating buildings, neon lights, holographic advertisements {{styleDescription}}"
"01-futuristic-city-skyline-2-","Futuristic city skyline","In the year 2050, cities looked very different.","aerial view of a sprawling megacity with interconnected skyscrapers, flying vehicles, vibrant energy streams {{styleDescription}}"
"02-advanced-ai-assistant-1-","Advanced AI assistant","AI assistants became an integral part of daily life.","hyper-realistic humanoid robot with glowing eyes assisting a person, surrounded by holographic interfaces {{styleDescription}}"
"02-advanced-ai-assistant-2-","Advanced AI assistant","AI assistants became an integral part of daily life.","sleek AI assistant device projecting a lifelike hologram, futuristic home interior, soft ambient lighting {{styleDescription}}"
```

## Quality Guidelines

- **Style Consistency**: Include style elements in every prompt
- **Vivid Language**: Use descriptive language for detailed, engaging images
- **Abstract Concepts**: Creatively represent essence visually
- **Concise but Detailed**: Balance brevity with sufficient detail
- **File Naming**: Sequential numbering with descriptive slugs

## Output Format

Write the complete CSV inside a code block.